The paper deals with forgetting in disjunctive logic programs, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the properties of forgetting, which is related to database theory (cs.DB). The practical definition of forgetting involves inference steps, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL) and computational logic (cs.CL).
